headline: Amcor to report fiscal 2025 third quarter results
summary: Amcor plc ("Amcor") (NYSE: AMCR, ASX: AMC) will announce its fiscal 2025 third quarter results for the three month period ended March 31, 2025, after the U.S. market closes on Wed., April 30, 2025.

headline: Amcor and Berry receive European Commission antitrust approval for combination
summary: Amcor plc ("Amcor") (NYSE: AMCR, ASX: AMC) and Berry Global Group, Inc. ("Berry") (NYSE: BERY) today announced the European Commission (EC) has granted unconditional approval under the EU Merger Regulation for the previously announced combination of the two companies, satisfying the final regulatory clearance required.
